creator: Syed Hasnain Bukhari
descriptionHtml:
Your new pet unicorn is waiting for you!

In My Unicorn - Virtual Pet game you can take care of unicorns and have fun playing mini games. Don't let your cute unicorn/littlepony get sad, give her all the love she needs and take care of little pony!
Change her appearance as you like and make it the most beautiful pet of all. Have fun in this unicorns free game for girls!

• Feed your baby unicorn pony with fruits and much more. Delicious!
• Cherish her to keep unicorn always happy. Unicorns sadden easily, give him all the love he needs!
• Bathe your unicorn pony to keep it clean. Unicorns are majestic creatures, don't let it look bad.
• Take her to bed when she needs energy to continue playing. You can also use the energy drink for super unicorns to restore all her energy quickly.
• Change the look of your pet unicorn as you like. You can choose between body color and eyes, hairstyles, horns, brands, tails and many more to come. Have the cutest unicorn in the world!
• Have fun playing exciting mini games with your magical unicorn pony and get coins to buy what you like the most.

MINIGAMES

Have fun playing exciting mini games and earn coins to buy items and food for your super unicorn pony!

• Jumps: Climb the platforms as high as you can without falling or touching a bomb. How tall can you get with your unicorn pony?
• Catch Fruits: Collect the falling fruits but be careful with the bombs!
• Stack Cakes: Help your pet unicorn stack as many cake floors as you can.
• Colored stars: Form lines with stars of the same color and reach the highest score.
• Food: Prepare hamburgers, drinks and side dishes for unicorns before time runs out.

And many more to come! Free mini games with updates of My baby Unicorn - Virtual Pet!

Start playing now with your pet unicorn game! It's free!

This is a free game, but it has items that can be purchased with real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased with real money.
